  <description>
    <p>
      Airshipper is the official launcher for Hobania, the online voxel-based RPG.
    </p>
    <p>
      Hobania is a multiplayer open world, voxel-based RPG written in Rust. It is inspired
      by games such as Cube World, Minecraft, Dwarf Fortress and Breath of the Wild.
    </p>
    <p>
      Hobania's development mainly happens pravatly.
      New contributors are always welcome!
    </p>
